reviewText: A great set a must for anyone's WEW collection. Still hosted by the great Eric Gargiulo. The set unfortunately it's very hard to find and very overpriced. But if you want to own them on a DVDRs with no artwork that is a possibility. This set has PPV# 29 nude battles, #30 nude submission, #31 nude takedown. Go to the WEW web site and you can order theses ppvs for $20 each on dvdr. Also fyi Eric Gargiulos last wew ppv is # 34 street fight.after that wew starts going down hill.by ppv#39 they start mixing old stuff with new.by ppv#45 its all old material! Hope my homework helps someone out there! Also if you can get your hands on the UK copies of the WEW dvds you will get the WHOLE UNCENSORED PAYPER VIEW UNLIKE THE US COPIES!
